    {
      "text": "Cyber Citizen Shockman Zero (Japanese: 改造町人シュビビンマン零, Hepburn: Kaizou Chōjin Shubibinman Zero) is a 1997 game for the Satellaview addon for the Super Famicom. It is a side-scrolling beat-'em-up developed by Masaya and published by NCS. It is the fourth and final game in the Cyber Citizen Shockman series, and the first on the SFC. The previous entries in the series were for the PC-Engine.",
